```typescript
// Good: Focus on actual code files
// Process: src/components/Header.tsx
// Process: src/App.tsx
// Process: tailwind.config.js (when discussing styling)
// Process: README.md (main project documentation)

// Ignore: PORTFOLIO_MIGRATION_PLAN.md
// Ignore: ai_context.md
// Ignore: testing_prompts.md
// Ignore: any_file_with_ai_keywords.md
// Ignore: context_notes.md
// Ignore: prompt_examples.md
```

This rule helps maintain focus on the actual development code and prevents the AI from getting distracted by documentation and non-essential files.
